æTo mark the terms of office of
CLLR CHERRY BEATH
as Mayor of Bath, June 2014 -June 2015,
and as Chair of Council, May 2017- May 2018.
Sit back awhile and reflect, take heart, and don't quit."⁄
◊Please sit, rest and reflect awhile. 
Graham Blacker, beloved husband, father and grandfather. 
And happy gardener. 
With always work to be done, but love, time and tenderness
bring beautiful rewards to cherish."Ð
